Monkey and the Crocodile

Once upon a time a monkey lived on a berry tree at the bank of a river in a jungle. In the same jungle, there lived a crocodile and his wife.
One day crocodile came to the bank of the river to rest under the tree.

The kind hearted monkey offered the crocodile some fruits. The crocodile really enjoyed them.

The crocodile started coming everyday and both of them became friends gradually.
One day the crocodile took some berries for his wife.
